    "description_long": "This is a red pickup truck with a bold, angular design and a black hood and roof. The vehicle features two passenger doors, silver and black striping along the sides, and a visible cargo bed at the rear. The wheels are metallic with a five-spoke design, and the windows are tinted gray. The front grille and headlights are integrated into the body, giving it a streamlined appearance. The rear of the truck includes a tailgate and subtle branding details. The overall look is sporty and utilitarian, suitable for both urban and off-road environments.",
